Augmenting LMs input with additional contexts retrieved from knowledge bases has been a popular approach to question answering (QA) [guu2020realm,petroni2020context], which shows that although LMs store information in billions of parameters, they still lack knowledge to answer knowledge-intensive questions, e.g., ``What is the appropriate color to wear at a Hindu funeral?''